<h2 class="section-title hidden stagger-2">Title Sequence Builder</h2>
<p class="section-desc hidden stagger-3">A 5-scene title sequence that plays end to end. Control timing, transitions, and style.</p>
<div class="ctrl-row hidden stagger-3">
